files.description: Folder of individual tables (.csv) containing training and test sets used during three-fold cross-validation. files.label: S3_File_A.zip

dataFile.description: Folders of individual tables (.csv) containing each training and test sets used during three-fold cross-validation: test sets, training sets before applying SMOTE, and training sets after applying SMOTE.
